      "pageid": 9709,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Magic Rock Candy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/File:Magic_Rock_Candy.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Magic Rock Candy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/25/Magic_Rock_Candy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic; padding-right: 3px;\">A rare and powerful candy infused with the essence of the prismatic shard.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0;\">Information</td>\n</tr>\n\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Source</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><ul><li><p><img alt=\"Desert Trader Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Desert_Trader_Icon.png/24px-Desert_Trader_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Desert_Trader_Icon.png/36px-Desert_Trader_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ed/Desert_Trader_Icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Desert_Trader\" title=\"Desert Trader\">Desert Trader</a></p></li><li><a href=\"/Haunted_Skull\" title=\"Haunted Skull\">Haunted Skull</a> drop (0.13%)</li><li><a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a></li><li><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Mystery Box.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/87/Mystery_Box.png/24px-Mystery_Box.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/87/Mystery_Box.png/36px-Mystery_Box.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/87/Mystery_Box.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Mystery_Box\" title=\"Mystery Box\">Mystery Box</a></span> (0.2%)</li><li><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Golden Mystery Box.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/fb/Golden_Mystery_Box.png/24px-Golden_Mystery_Box.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/fb/Golden_Mystery_Box.png/36px-Golden_Mystery_Box.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/fb/Golden_Mystery_Box.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Golden_Mystery_Box\" title=\"Golden Mystery Box\">Golden Mystery Box</a></span> (0.4%)</li><li><a href=\"/Giant_Stump#Raccoon_Wife.27s_Shop\" title=\"Giant Stump\">Raccoon Wife's Shop</a></li></ul></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Buff(s)</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Mining.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/41/Mining.png/24px-Mining.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/41/Mining.png/36px-Mining.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/41/Mining.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Mining\" title=\"Mining\">Mining</a>&#160;(+2)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Luck.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f0/Luck.png/24px-Luck.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f0/Luck.png/36px-Luck.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/f0/Luck.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Luck\" title=\"Luck\">Luck</a>&#160;(+5)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Speed.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Speed.png/24px-Speed.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Speed.png/36px-Speed.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/94/Speed.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Speed\" title=\"Speed\">Speed</a>&#160;(+1)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Defense.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/66/Defense.png/24px-Defense.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/66/Defense.png/36px-Defense.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/66/Defense.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Defense\" title=\"Defense\">Defense</a>&#160;(+5)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Attack.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/00/Attack.png/24px-Attack.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/00/Attack.png/36px-Attack.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/00/Attack.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Attack\" title=\"Attack\">Attack</a>&#160;(+5)</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Buff Duration</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120974\">.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .durationtemplate img,.mw-parser-output .durationtemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"durationtemplate\"><img alt=\"Time Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/24px-Time_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/70/Time_Icon.png/36px-Time_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/70/Time_Icon.png 2x\" /> 8m 24s</span></td>\n\t</tr>\n\t<tr>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\"><a href=\"/Energy\" title=\"Energy\">Energy</a> / <a href=\"/Health\" title=\"Health\">Health</a></td>\n\t\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\">\n\t\t\t\t<table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 20px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Energy.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/20px-Energy.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/30px-Energy.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Energy.png/40px-Energy.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td style=\"vertical-align: bottom; padding-right: 6px;\">500</td>\n\t\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 20px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Health.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/20px-Health.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/30px-Health.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Health.png/40px-Health.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t\t<td style=\"vertical-align: bottom;\">225</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t</tr> \n\t<tr>\n\t<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Sell Price</td>\n\t\t<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"5000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />5,000g</span>\n\t\t</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>Magic Rock Candy</b> is a special edible item that can be obtained in variety of ways.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Locations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Locations</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Gifting\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gifting</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Bundles\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Bundles</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Tailoring\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tailoring</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quests\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quests</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Locations\">Locations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Magic_Rock_Candy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Locations\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Dropped by <a href=\"/Haunted_Skull\" title=\"Haunted Skull\">Haunted Skulls</a> (0.13% chance).</li>\n<li>Opening <a href=\"/Mystery_Box\" title=\"Mystery Box\">Mystery Boxes</a> (0.2% chance) or <a href=\"/Golden_Mystery_Box\" title=\"Golden Mystery Box\">Golden Mystery Boxes</a> (0.4% chance).</li>\n<li>One can be purchased each <a href=\"/Days_of_the_Week#Thursday\" title=\"Days of the Week\">Thursday</a> from the <a href=\"/Desert_Trader\" title=\"Desert Trader\">Desert Trader</a> for 3 <a href=\"/Prismatic_Shard\" title=\"Prismatic Shard\">Prismatic Shards</a>.</li>\n<li>Can be purchased from the <a href=\"/Giant_Stump#Raccoon_Wife.27s_Shop\" title=\"Giant Stump\">Raccoon Wife's Shop</a> for 20 <a href=\"/Golden_Mystery_Box\" title=\"Golden Mystery Box\">Golden Mystery Boxes</a> after the 6th Raccoon family request is completed and <a href=\"/Mastery_Cave#Masteries\" title=\"Mastery Cave\">Foraging Mastery</a> has been claimed.</li>\n<li>As the reward for donating 90 items to the <a href=\"/Museum\" title=\"Museum\">Museum</a>.</li>\n<li>As the 22nd item received from the <a href=\"/Mayor%27s_Manor#Prize_Machine\" title=\"Mayor&#39;s Manor\">prize machine</a> in <a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\">Lewis</a>'s <a href=\"/Mayor%27s_Manor\" title=\"Mayor&#39;s Manor\">manor</a>.</li>\n<li>One is sold by the <a href=\"/Desert_Festival#Calico_Egg_Merchant\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Calico Egg Merchant</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"250\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Calico Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/da/Calico_Egg.png/24px-Calico_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/da/Calico_Egg.png/36px-Calico_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/da/Calico_Egg.png 2x\" /> 250</span> <a href=\"/Calico_Egg\" title=\"Calico Egg\">Calico Eggs</a> on the last day of the <a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a>.</li>\n<li>One is sold by <a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\">Jas</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"300\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Calico Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/da/Calico_Egg.png/24px-Calico_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/da/Calico_Egg.png/36px-Calico_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/da/Calico_Egg.png 2x\" /> 300</span> Calico Eggs whenever she is hosting a <a href=\"/Desert_Festival#Villager_Shops\" title=\"Desert Festival\">shop</a> at the <a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a>.</li>\n<li>One is rewarded for submitting an <a href=\"/Desert_Festival#Skull_Cavern\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Egg Rating</a> of 55-999 to <a href=\"/Gil\" title=\"Gil\">Gil</a> during the Desert Festival.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gifting\">Gifting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Magic_Rock_Candy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Gifting\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Villager Reactions\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Love\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\"><img alt=\"Abigail Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/63/Abigail_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Abigail\" title=\"Abigail\">Abigail</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Alex\" title=\"Alex\"><img alt=\"Alex Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Alex_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Alex\" title=\"Alex\">Alex</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Caroline\" title=\"Caroline\"><img alt=\"Caroline Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Caroline_Icon.png\" decod